This reproducibility report provides details about the artifact evaluation done with regards to the Artifact Description and Evaluation appendix of SC25 paper Numerical Performance of the Implicitly Restarted Arnoldi Method in OFP8, Bfloat16, Posit, and Takum Arithmetics by Hunhold et al. The work was done as part of the Reproducibility Initiative of SC25. The author is a member of the SC25 Reproducibilty Committee.